from sklearn.metrics import precision_recall_fscore_support
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score
from sklearn.metrics import classification_report ,confusion_matrix ,ConfusionMatrixDisplay

from sklearn.linear_model import LogisticRegression
LR = LogisticRegression()
LR.fit(x_train,y_train)
y_pred = LR.predict(x_test)
print(classification_report(y_test, y_pred.reshape(-1,1)))
cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred.reshape(-1,1))
print(cm)
disp = ConfusionMatrixDisplay(confusion_matrix=cm)
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
disp.plot(ax=ax,cmap='Blues')

from sklearn import svm
clf = svm.SVC() 
clf.fit(x_train, y_train)
y_pred = clf.predict(x_test)
print(classification_report(y_test, y_pred.reshape(-1,1)))
cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, y_pred.reshape(-1,1))
print(cm)
disp = ConfusionMatrixDisplay(confusion_matrix=cm)
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
disp.plot(ax=ax,cmap='Blues')

#print(accuracy_measure(y_test,yhat))
print(classification_report(y_test, yhat.reshape(-1,1)))
cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, yhat.reshape(-1,1))
print(cm)
disp = ConfusionMatrixDisplay(confusion_matrix=cm)
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
disp.plot(ax=ax,cmap='Blues')

from sklearn.ensemble import RandomForestClassifier
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score

yhat=model.predict(x_test)
#print(accuracy_measure(y_test,yhat))

cm = confusion_matrix(y_test, yhat.reshape(-1,1))
print(cm)

fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
disp.plot(ax=ax,cmap='Blues')

print(cm)
disp = ConfusionMatrixDisplay(confusion_matrix=cm)
fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(8,6))
disp.plot(ax=ax,cmap='Blues')
